# [[of]]/[[from]] [[whom]]/[[which]], [[whose]]; [[whereof]]
#: {{ux|fr|Vous rappelez-vous ce '''dont''' je vous ai parlé ?|Do you remember that '''of which''' we spoke?}}
#: {{ux|fr|Il n’est rien '''dont''' je sois encore certain.|There is nothing '''of which''' I am still certain.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Quel est le pays '''dont''' provient cette marchandise suspecte ?|What is the country '''from which''' the suspicious merchandise comes?}}
#: {{ux|fr|J’ai décidé d’abandonner l’affaire '''dont''' je vous ai entretenu il y a quelques jours.|I decided to abandon the matter '''of which''' we have been speaking for a few days.}}
#: {{ux|fr|La maladie '''dont''' il est mort porte un nom imprononçable.|The disease '''of which''' he died has an unpronounceable name.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Les pays '''dont''' nous n’avons point de connaissance sont les destinations privilégiées des grands aventuriers.|The countries '''of which''' we have little knowledge are the privileged destinations of great adventurers.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Ces étoiles — '''dont''' le nom m’échappe — sont les plus brillantes de la voûte céleste.|These stars, '''whose''' names escape me, are the brightest in the skies.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Le Québec est une province du Canada '''dont''' les frontières correspondent au territoire de la nation québécoise.|Quebec is a province of Canada '''whose''' borders correspond to the Quebecois nation.}}
# {{lb|fr|sometimes}} [[by]] [[which]]
#: {{ux|fr|Le coup '''dont''' il fut frappé.|The blow '''by which''' he was struck.}}
# {{n-g|Denotes a part of a set, may be translated as "[[including]]" or ''[[such as]]'' in some situations.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Il a eu dix enfants, '''dont''' neuf filles.|He had ten children, nine '''of them''' girls.}}

